This article is a personal reflection by the wife of President Joe Biden, reflecting on his journey to the presidency and his commitment to building a better America. She highlights his resilience, determination, and ability to bring people together. She discusses the importance of investing in industries of the future, providing opportunities for working families, and removing barriers for women in STEM fields. She also mentions the American Rescue Plan and its impact on creating jobs and changing lives. The author emphasizes the importance of individual contributions in building a better America and expresses gratitude for the faith placed in Joe Biden. She concludes by stating that Biden's leadership will lead the country forward to a better America, with the involvement and support of its citizens.